{"tid":1996781,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【大飢荒?】聯合國世界糧食計劃署在中國啟動全球人道主義應急樞紐","createTime":"2020-05-01T07:36:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-01T08:02:21.000Z","uid":66087,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"05a4b25568b528727296c4b88cb32474166621a0","tid":1996781,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T07:36:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tech.sina.com.cn/roll/2020-04-30/doc-iirczymi9269515.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftech.sina.com.cn%2Froll%2F2020-04-30%2Fdoc-iirczymi9269515.shtml&d=IJrjZyikD9iZithZGIL3rEYnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=bbeeec59\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tech.sina.com.cn/roll/2020-04-30/doc-iirczymi9269515.shtml</a><br />\n<br />\n在中國政府的支持下，近日，聯合國世界糧食計劃署在中國啟動全球人道主義應急樞紐。<br />\n<br />\n聯合國中國樞紐將承擔國際社會在華採購物資的倉儲、整合以及緊急空運的任務，使救援物資迅速地送達世界各地，或直接到達受影響的地區。<br />\n<br />\n為快速啟動這一樞紐，阿里菜鳥提供了倉儲等物流支持。目前，首批抗疫醫療物資已於4月底運抵位於廣州的倉庫樞紐。<br />\n<br />\n聯合國世界糧食計劃署駐華代表屈四喜表示：&ldquo;憑藉其領先的製造業、完善的供應鏈和技術創新， 中國擁有設立應急樞紐獨特的優勢。該樞紐將在應對疫情過程中發揮十分重要的作用。&rdquo; <br />\n<br />\n據悉，阿里菜鳥全球物流網絡迄今已為全球運輸醫療物資超億件，三四月為中小企業提供貨運包機近200架次。"},{"pid":"4cc061c63ba78ad87fd5ec99ac530ede0928008a","tid":1996781,"uid":294518,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T07:39:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />想控制全球物資！邊個仲信佢？佢可能死得仲快啲"},{"pid":"56e1bc88ce89b77f411d560933855ecd410483f4","tid":1996781,"uid":235152,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T07:56:21.000Z","msg":"連豬肉都要走私,同人講大把糧食送,送黃豆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26e5836a91c8c4c8dd51dddac4bc252cb32412be","tid":1996781,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T07:59:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5hKPhnD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5hKPhnD.jpg&h=ec328b4d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7d685a9fc1709a82be083c296c276447592bc7df","tid":1996781,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"26e5836a91c8c4c8dd51dddac4bc252cb32412be","tid":1996781,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T07:59:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5hKPhnD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5hKPhnD.jpg&h=ec328b4d&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T08:02:21.000Z","msg":"KFC 比羊肉串取代<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原來呢個就係習大大嘅中國夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}